exercises.name: Bench Press
exercises.description: Classic chest exercise performed with a barbell
exercises.instructions: Lie on bench, grip bar slightly wider than shoulders, lower to chest, press up
exercises.tips: Keep feet flat on floor, maintain arch in back, control the weight

exercises.name: Incline Dumbbell Press
exercises.instructions: Set bench to 30-45 degree incline, press dumbbells up and together
exercises.tips: Focus on upper chest, keep core tight, control the negative

exercises.name: Push-ups
exercises.instructions: Start in plank position, lower chest to ground, push back up
exercises.tips: Keep body straight, engage core, full range of motion

exercises.name: Pull-ups
exercises.instructions: Hang from bar, pull body up until chin clears bar, lower slowly
exercises.tips: Engage lats, avoid swinging, full range of motion

exercises.name: Barbell Rows
exercises.instructions: Bend forward, pull bar to lower chest, squeeze shoulder blades
exercises.tips: Keep back straight, pull with elbows, control the weight

exercises.name: Lat Pulldown
exercises.instructions: Pull bar to upper chest, squeeze lats, return slowly
exercises.tips: Lean back slightly, pull with lats not arms, full stretch

exercises.name: Overhead Press
exercises.instructions: Press bar from shoulder height to overhead, lower with control
exercises.tips: Keep core tight, press straight up, full range of motion

exercises.name: Lateral Raises
exercises.instructions: Raise arms to sides until parallel to floor, lower slowly
exercises.tips: Slight bend in elbows, control the weight, avoid swinging

exercises.name: Rear Delt Flyes
exercises.instructions: Bend forward, raise arms to sides, squeeze rear delts
exercises.tips: Keep slight bend in elbows, focus on rear delts, control movement

exercises.name: Bicep Curls
exercises.instructions: Curl weights up, squeeze biceps, lower slowly
exercises.tips: Keep elbows at sides, full range of motion, control the negative

exercises.name: Tricep Dips
exercises.instructions: Lower body using arms, push back up, keep elbows close
exercises.tips: Keep body upright, full range of motion, control the movement

exercises.name: Hammer Curls
exercises.instructions: Curl with neutral grip, squeeze biceps, lower slowly
exercises.tips: Keep wrists neutral, full range of motion, control the weight

exercises.name: Squats
exercises.instructions: Lower until thighs parallel to floor, drive through heels to stand
exercises.tips: Keep chest up, knees track over toes, full depth

exercises.name: Romanian Deadlifts
exercises.description: Hip hinge movement for posterior chain
exercises.instructions: Hinge at hips, lower bar along legs, return to standing
exercises.tips: Keep back straight, feel stretch in hamstrings, drive hips forward

exercises.name: Walking Lunges
exercises.instructions: Step forward into lunge, push back up, alternate legs
exercises.tips: Keep torso upright, full range of motion, control the movement

exercises.name: Leg Press
exercises.instructions: Push platform away, lower with control, drive through heels
exercises.tips: Keep knees aligned, full range of motion, control the weight

exercises.name: Hip Thrusts
exercises.instructions: Drive hips up, squeeze glutes, lower with control
exercises.tips: Keep core tight, drive through heels, full hip extension

exercises.name: Glute Bridges
exercises.instructions: Lift hips up, squeeze glutes, lower slowly
exercises.tips: Keep feet close to glutes, drive through heels, squeeze at top

exercises.name: Bulgarian Split Squats
exercises.description: Single leg glute and quad exercise
exercises.instructions: Rear foot elevated, lower into lunge, drive up through front heel
exercises.tips: Keep torso upright, full range of motion, control the movement

exercises.name: Cable Kickbacks
exercises.instructions: Kick leg back, squeeze glute, return slowly
exercises.tips: Keep core tight, focus on glute contraction, control the movement

exercises.name: Plank
exercises.instructions: Hold straight line from head to heels, engage core
exercises.tips: Keep body straight, breathe normally, engage entire core

exercises.name: Dead Bug
exercises.instructions: Lower opposite arm and leg, return to start, alternate
exercises.tips: Keep lower back pressed to floor, move slowly, maintain tension

exercises.name: Russian Twists
exercises.instructions: Rotate torso side to side, keep feet off ground
exercises.tips: Keep core tight, control the rotation, full range of motion

exercises.name: Box Jumps
exercises.instructions: Jump onto box, step down, repeat
exercises.tips: Land softly, full hip extension, control the landing

exercises.name: Burpees
exercises.instructions: Drop to push-up, jump feet to hands, jump up
exercises.tips: Maintain form, control the movement, full range of motion

exercises.name: Mountain Climbers
exercises.instructions: Alternate bringing knees to chest in plank position
exercises.tips: Keep core tight, maintain plank position, quick movements

exercises.instructions: Stand with feet together, arms at sides. Jump up spreading feet shoulder-width apart while raising arms overhead. Jump back to starting position.
exercises.tips: Keep core engaged, land softly on balls of feet

exercises.name: High knees
exercises.description: Running in place with high knee lifts
exercises.instructions: Run in place, bringing knees up towards chest. Pump arms naturally.
exercises.tips: Maintain upright posture, engage core

exercises.name: Bodyweight squats
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width apart. Lower down as if sitting back into a chair, then return to standing.
exercises.tips: Keep chest up, knees tracking over toes

exercises.name: Walking lunges
exercises.instructions: Step forward into lunge position, lower back knee towards ground, then step forward with other leg.
exercises.tips: Keep torso upright, don't let front knee go past toes

exercises.name: Arm circles
exercises.instructions: Extend arms to sides, make small circles forward and backward.
exercises.tips: Keep movements controlled, don't force range of motion

exercises.name: Inchworm walkouts
exercises.instructions: From standing, bend forward and walk hands out to plank position, then walk hands back to feet.
exercises.tips: Keep legs straight, engage core throughout

exercises.name: Arm swings
exercises.instructions: Swing arms forward and backward in large circles.
exercises.tips: Start small, gradually increase range of motion

exercises.name: Shoulder rolls
exercises.instructions: Roll shoulders forward and backward in circular motion.
exercises.tips: Move slowly and controlled

exercises.name: Dynamic chest opener
exercises.instructions: Extend arms to sides, bring them forward and back in controlled motion.
exercises.tips: Feel stretch across chest

exercises.name: Light jogging on the spot
exercises.instructions: Jog in place with light, bouncy steps.
exercises.tips: Stay light on feet, pump arms naturally

exercises.name: Glute bridges
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, knees bent, feet flat. Lift hips up squeezing glutes at top.
exercises.tips: Hold at top for 2 seconds, squeeze glutes hard

exercises.name: Clam shells
exercises.instructions: Lie on side, knees bent. Keep feet together, lift top knee up.
exercises.tips: Don't let hips roll back, focus on glute activation

exercises.name: Monster walks
exercises.instructions: Squat position, take lateral steps while maintaining squat.
exercises.tips: Keep knees tracking over toes, stay low

exercises.name: Hip thrust
exercises.instructions: Sit with upper back against bench, barbell across hips. Drive hips up squeezing glutes.
exercises.tips: Hold at top, squeeze glutes hard, control descent

exercises.name: Squat
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width apart, barbell on back. Lower down as if sitting back, then drive up.
exercises.tips: Keep chest up, knees tracking over toes, drive through heels

exercises.name: Romanian deadlift
exercises.instructions: Stand holding barbell, hinge at hips keeping legs straighter, lower bar down legs, return to standing.
exercises.tips: Keep chest up, feel stretch in hamstrings

exercises.name: Bulgarian split squat
exercises.instructions: Stand in front of bench, place rear foot on bench. Lower down into lunge position, drive up.
exercises.tips: Keep front knee tracking over toe, don't let it cave in

exercises.name: Glute kickbacks
exercises.instructions: Attach cable to ankle, kick back against resistance focusing on glute contraction.
exercises.tips: Keep core engaged, don't swing the leg

exercises.name: Abductor machine
exercises.instructions: Sit in abductor machine, push legs out against resistance, return to start.
exercises.tips: Control the movement, don't let legs snap back

exercises.name: Scapula retractions
exercises.instructions: On cable machine, pull shoulder blades back and together without bending elbows.
exercises.tips: Focus on squeezing shoulder blades together

exercises.name: Resistance band face pulls
exercises.description: Posterior deltoid and upper trap exercise
exercises.instructions: Hold band at face level, pull towards face separating hands at end.
exercises.tips: Keep elbows high, focus on external rotation

exercises.name: Lat pulldown
exercises.instructions: Sit at lat pulldown machine, pull bar down to chest, control return.
exercises.tips: Keep chest up, pull with lats not arms

exercises.name: Seated row
exercises.instructions: Sit at rowing machine, pull handle to torso, squeeze shoulder blades together.
exercises.tips: Keep chest up, pull elbows back

exercises.name: Dumbbell single-arm row
exercises.instructions: Bend over bench, row dumbbell to hip, control descent.
exercises.tips: Keep core engaged, don't rotate torso

exercises.name: Triceps pushdowns
exercises.instructions: Stand at cable machine, push bar down extending arms, control return.
exercises.tips: Keep elbows at sides, don't swing the weight

exercises.name: Overhead triceps extension
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbell overhead, lower behind head, extend back up.
exercises.tips: Keep elbows pointing forward, don't flare them out

exercises.name: Dips
exercises.instructions: Support body on bench, lower down by bending elbows, push back up.
exercises.tips: Keep chest up, don't go too low if it hurts shoulders

exercises.name: Chest press machine
exercises.instructions: Sit in chest press machine, push handles forward, control return.
exercises.tips: Keep shoulder blades back, don't let shoulders roll forward

exercises.name: Pec deck
exercises.instructions: Sit in pec deck machine, bring arms together in front of chest, control return.
exercises.tips: Keep slight bend in elbows, feel stretch across chest

exercises.name: Band pull-aparts
exercises.instructions: Hold band in front, pull apart bringing hands to sides.
exercises.tips: Keep arms straight, focus on rear delts

exercises.name: Front raises
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells, raise arms to front to shoulder height, control descent.
exercises.tips: Keep slight bend in elbows, don't swing the weight

exercises.name: Shoulder press machine
exercises.instructions: Sit in shoulder press machine, press handles overhead, control return.
exercises.tips: Keep core engaged, don't arch back excessively

exercises.name: Lateral raises
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells, raise arms to sides to shoulder height, control descent.
exercises.tips: Keep slight bend in elbows, lead with pinkies

exercises.name: Arnold press
exercises.instructions: Start with dumbbells at shoulders, rotate and press overhead, reverse the motion.
exercises.tips: Control the rotation, don't rush the movement

exercises.name: Biceps curls
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells, curl up to shoulders, control descent.
exercises.tips: Keep elbows at sides, don't swing the weight

exercises.name: Hammer curls
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells with neutral grip, curl up to shoulders, control descent.
exercises.tips: Keep wrists straight, focus on biceps contraction

exercises.name: Bicycle crunches
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, bring knees to chest, alternate touching elbow to opposite knee.
exercises.tips: Keep lower back pressed to ground, don't pull on neck

exercises.name: Leg raises
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, raise legs up to 90 degrees, lower with control.
exercises.tips: Keep lower back pressed to ground, don't swing legs

exercises.name: Russian twists
exercises.instructions: Sit with knees bent, lean back slightly, rotate torso side to side.
exercises.tips: Keep chest up, don't round shoulders

exercises.name: Heel touches
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, knees bent, reach to touch heels alternately.
exercises.tips: Keep shoulders off ground, don't pull on neck

exercises.name: Reverse crunches
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, bring knees to chest, lift hips off ground.
exercises.tips: Keep lower back pressed to ground, control the movement

exercises.name: Side plank
exercises.instructions: Lie on side, support body on forearm, hold straight line.
exercises.tips: Keep hips up, don't let them sag

exercises.name: Mountain climbers
exercises.instructions: Start in plank, alternate bringing knees to chest quickly.
exercises.tips: Keep core engaged, maintain plank position

exercises.name: Jump squats
exercises.instructions: Perform squat, then explode up into jump, land softly.
exercises.tips: Land softly, keep knees tracking over toes

exercises.name: Jump rope
exercises.instructions: Jump over rope with both feet, maintain rhythm.
exercises.tips: Stay light on feet, keep core engaged

exercises.name: Sprint in place
exercises.instructions: Run in place at maximum intensity, pump arms.
exercises.tips: Maintain high intensity, keep core engaged

exercises.name: Leg swings
exercises.instructions: Stand next to wall, swing leg forward and backward in controlled motion
exercises.tips: Keep core engaged, don't force the range of motion

exercises.name: Banded lateral walks
exercises.instructions: Place band around legs above knees, take lateral steps while maintaining tension
exercises.tips: Keep tension on band, don't let knees cave in

exercises.name: Ankle mobility
exercises.instructions: Move ankle in circles and up/down motions
exercises.tips: Move slowly, don't force range of motion

exercises.name: Clamshells with band
exercises.description: Hip and glute activation with resistance band
exercises.instructions: Lie on side with band around knees, lift top knee up against resistance
exercises.tips: Don't let hips roll back, focus on glute activation

exercises.name: Standing calf raises
exercises.instructions: Stand on edge of step, raise up on toes, lower down below step level
exercises.tips: Control the movement, feel stretch in calves

exercises.name: Shoulder shrugs
exercises.description: Upper trap and shoulder mobility exercise
exercises.instructions: Lift shoulders up towards ears, roll them back and down
exercises.tips: Move slowly and controlled, don't force range of motion

exercises.name: Light dumbbell rows
exercises.instructions: Hold light dumbbells, row to sides focusing on shoulder blade movement
exercises.tips: Keep movements controlled, focus on activation

exercises.name: Dumbbell bicep curl
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells, curl up to shoulders, control descent
exercises.tips: Keep elbows at sides, don't swing the weight

exercises.name: Cable tricep pushdown
exercises.instructions: Stand at cable machine, push bar down extending arms, control return
exercises.tips: Keep elbows at sides, don't swing the weight

exercises.name: Overhead dumbbell tricep extension
exercises.description: Triceps isolation exercise with dumbbell overhead
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbell overhead with both hands, lower behind head, extend back up
exercises.tips: Keep elbows pointing forward, don't flare them out

exercises.name: Hanging knee raises
exercises.description: Lower ab exercise hanging from bar
exercises.instructions: Hang from bar, bring knees up to chest, lower with control
exercises.tips: Keep core engaged, don't swing the legs

exercises.name: Glute bridge march
exercises.description: Dynamic glute bridge with alternating leg lifts
exercises.instructions: Start in glute bridge position, lift one leg up, lower and alternate
exercises.tips: Keep hips up throughout, don't let them drop

exercises.name: Light dumbbell chest press
exercises.instructions: Hold light dumbbells, press up and out, control descent
exercises.tips: Keep movements controlled, focus on activation

exercises.name: Dumbbell chest press
exercises.instructions: Lie on bench, press dumbbells up from chest, control descent
exercises.tips: Keep shoulder blades back, don't let shoulders roll forward

exercises.name: Hip circles
exercises.instructions: Stand on one leg, make circles with the other leg, switch sides
exercises.tips: Keep movements controlled, don't force range of motion

exercises.name: Side lunges
exercises.instructions: Step to the side, lower into lunge position, return to center
exercises.tips: Keep chest up, don't let knee cave in

exercises.name: Donkey kicks
exercises.instructions: Start on hands and knees, kick one leg back and up, return
exercises.tips: Keep core engaged, don't arch back

exercises.name: Banded side steps
exercises.instructions: Place band around legs, take lateral steps while maintaining tension
exercises.tips: Keep tension on band, don't let knees cave in

exercises.name: Dumbbell lunges
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells, step forward into lunge, return to start
exercises.tips: Keep torso upright, don't let front knee go past toes

exercises.name: Step-ups with dumbbells
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells, step up onto platform, step down
exercises.tips: Control the movement, don't use momentum

exercises.name: Shoulder rotations
exercises.instructions: Rotate shoulders forward and backward in circular motion
exercises.tips: Move slowly and controlled

exercises.name: Scapular retractions
exercises.instructions: Squeeze shoulder blades together and back
exercises.tips: Focus on bringing shoulder blades together

exercises.name: Torso twists
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet hip-width apart, rotate torso side to side
exercises.tips: Keep hips facing forward, rotate from the spine

exercises.name: Light lat pull-down
exercises.instructions: Light weight lat pulldown focusing on activation
exercises.tips: Keep movements controlled, focus on activation

exercises.name: Triceps kickbacks
exercises.instructions: Bend over, extend arms back, squeeze triceps
exercises.tips: Keep elbows at sides, don't swing the weight

exercises.name: Triceps rope pushdown
exercises.instructions: Stand at cable machine with rope, push down extending arms
exercises.tips: Keep elbows at sides, don't swing the weight

exercises.name: Clamshell with band

exercises.instructions: Lie on side with band around knees, lift top knee up
exercises.tips: Don't let hips roll back, focus on glute activation

exercises.name: Hip abduction with band
exercises.instructions: Place band around legs, abduct legs against resistance

exercises.name: Single-leg glute bridge
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, lift one leg, bridge up with other leg
exercises.tips: Keep core engaged, don't let hips drop

exercises.name: Chest openers
exercises.instructions: Extend arms to sides, bring them forward and back
exercises.tips: Feel stretch across chest

exercises.name: Light dumbbell curls
exercises.instructions: Hold light dumbbells, curl up to shoulders
exercises.tips: Keep movements controlled, focus on activation

exercises.name: Weighted crunch
exercises.instructions: Hold weight to chest, perform crunches
exercises.tips: Keep lower back pressed to ground

exercises.name: Treadmill
exercises.instructions: Walk or run on treadmill at light pace
exercises.tips: Maintain steady pace, focus on breathing

exercises.name: Shoulder circles
exercises.instructions: Rotate shoulders forward and backward in circular motion
exercises.tips: Move slowly and controlled

exercises.name: Trunk rotations

exercises.name: Triceps extensions

exercises.name: Stretch legs
exercises.instructions: Stretch hamstrings, quads, and calves
exercises.tips: Hold each stretch for 30-60 seconds

exercises.name: Stretch back
exercises.instructions: Perform cat-cow or seated twist stretches

exercises.instructions: Perform chest opener and shoulder stretches
